column1: #Text=Saw one at a traveling show once .
#Text=" Due says : " Bet he tastes a lot like possum chicken .
#Text=" Tho says : " You think everything tastes like possum chicken .
#Text=" Tho says : " What 'd you say that fer ?
#Text=" Tho says : " But you do n't have to tell 'em that .
#Text=" Due says : " Well how 'd I know they 'd understand me ?
